comments.raw_text:
in pkix_pl_OcspResponse_VerifySignature:

> if (signature->wasChecked) {
>     if (signature->status == SECSuccess) {
>         response->signerCert =
>             CERT_DupCertificate(signature->cert);
>     } else { ... }
> }
> 
> response->signerCert = 
>     ocsp_GetSignerCertificate(response->handle, tbsData,
                              signature, issuerCert);

notice that response->signerCert is assigned twice, without a call to CERT_DestroyCertificate in between.

